reviews.review_text: The Dead's last stand at MWPP.....  Trouble ahead Jerry in Red. Legendary 2nd set "Shakedown" opener with bobby riding his tremelo and Jerry and co. tearing it up. This is a prime example of why I love good audience recordings,had a pair of AKG's myself for over  a decade. about 8 minutes into this beastly 13+ minute "Shakedown" the audience is literally going crazy and the energy that was feeding between band and crowd was literally incredible.                                                                      Twas their last show at the storied venue,but they went out guns a blazing, YOWSY!
